RequestBody.prompt: A drawing of the Seattle skyline in the style of Van Gogh

data.revised_prompt: A finely detailed interpretation of the Seattle skyline. The scene incorporates the use of post-impressionistic elements inspired by Van Gogh. Expect swirling, vivid color patterns, rich textures, and bold lines reminiscent of Van Gogh's 'Starry Night'. The towering structures, Sky View Observatory of the Columbia Center, Space Needle, and the iconic Ferris Wheel on the waterfront, they all come together to form an artistic panorama. The sky carries the energy with dashes of royal blue and gold, while the structures display a captivating interplay of light and shadow.
